6433 	}
6434

6438 In2iGui.Alert.prototype = {
6439 	show : function() {
6440 		var zIndex = In2iGui.nextAlertIndex();
6441 		if (this.options.modal) {
6442 			In2iGui.showCurtain(this,zIndex);
6443 			zIndex++;
6444 		}

6446 		this.element.style.display='block';
6447 		this.element.style.top=(n2i.getScrollTop()+100)+'px';
6448 		n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,200);

6467 		}

6469 	},

6476 			this.body.removeClassName(this.emotion);
6477 		}
6478 		this.emotion = emotion;
6479 		this.body.addClassName(emotion);
6480 	},

6482 		options = options || {};
6483 		this.setTitle(options.title || null);
6484 		this.setText(options.text || null);
6485 		this.setVariant(options.variant || null);
6486 		this.setEmotion(options.emotion || null);
6487 	},

6491 			this.body.appendChild(this.buttons);

6506 In2iGui.Button.create = function(name,o) {
6507 	var o = n2i.override({text:'',highlighted:false,enabled:true},o);
6508 	var className = 'in2igui_button'+(o.highlighted ? ' in2igui_button_highlighted' : '');
6509 	if (!o.enabled) className+=' in2igui_button_disabled';
6510 	var element = new Element('a',{'class':className,href:'#'});
6511 	var element2 = new Element('span');
6512 	element.appendChild(element2);
6513 	var element3 = new Element('span');
6514 	element2.appendChild(element3);
6515 	if (o.icon) {
6516 		var icon = new Element('em',{'class':'in2igui_button_icon'}).setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(o.icon,1)+')'});
6517 		if (!o.text || o.text.length==0) {
6518 			icon.addClassName('in2igui_button_icon_notext');
6519 		}
6520 		element3.insert(icon);
6521 	}
6522 	if (o.text && o.text.length>0) {
6523 		element3.insert(o.text);
6524 	}
6525 	if (o.title && o.title.length>0) {
6526 		element3.insert(o.title);
6527 	}
6528 	return new In2iGui.Button(element,name);
6529 }

6601 In2iGui.Selection.prototype = {
6602 	getValue : function() {
6603 		return this.value;
6604 	},
6605 	getSelection : function() {
6606 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
6607 			if (this.items[i].value == this.value) {
6608 				return this.items[i];
6609 			}
6610 		};
6611 		for (var i=0; i < this.subItems.length; i++) {
6612 			var item = this.subItems[i].getSelection();
6613 			if (item) return item;
6614 		};
6615 	},
6616 	setValue : function(value) {
6617 		this.value = value;
6618 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
6619 			var item = this.items[i];
6620 			item.element.setClassName('selected',(item.value==value));
6621 		};
6622 		this.subItems.each(function(sub) {
6623 			sub.updateUI();
6624 		});
6625 	},
6626 	changeValue : function(value) {
6627 		this.setValue(value);
6628 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectorSelectionChanged'); // deprecated
6629 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectionChanged',this.value); // deprecated
6630 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'onSelectionChange',this.value);
6631 		In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'value',this.value);
6632 	},
6633 	registerItems : function(items) {
6634 		items.selection = this;
6635 		this.subItems.push(items);
6636 	},
6637 	registerItem : function(id,title,icon,badge,value,kind) {
6638 		var element = $(id);
6639 		element.in2iGuiValue = value;
6640 		this.items.push({id:id,title:title,icon:icon,badge:badge,element:element,value:value,kind:kind});
6641 		var self = this;
6642 		element.onclick = function() {
6643 			self.itemWasClicked(value);
6644 		}
6645 		element.ondblclick = function() {
6646 			self.itemWasDoubleClicked();
6647 			return false;
6648 		}
6649 		element.dragDropInfo = {kind:kind,value:value};
6650 		element.addClassName('droppable');
6651 		element.observe('mouseover',In2iGui.dropOverListener);
6652 		element.observe('mouseout',In2iGui.dropOutListener);
6653 	},
6654 	
6655 	setObjects : function(items) {
6656 		var self = this;
6657 		items.each(function(item) {
6658 			self.items.push(item);
6659 			var node = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_item'});
6660 			item.element = node;
6661 			self.element.insert(node);
6662 			var inner = new Element('span').update(item.title);
6663 			if (item.icon) {
6664 				inner.setStyle({'backgroundImage' : 'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(item.icon,1)+')'}).addClassName('in2igui_icon');
6665 			}
6666 			node.insert(inner);
6667 			node.observe('click',function() {
6668 				self.changeValue(item.value);
6669 			});
6670 			node.observe('dblclick',function() {
6671 				self.itemWasDoubleClicked();
6672 				return false;
6673 			});
6674 		});
6675 	},
6676 	
6677 	// Events
6678 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
6679 		this.changeValue(value);
6680 	},
6681 	itemWasDoubleClicked : function() {
6682 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectorObjectWasOpened');
6683 	}
6684 }

6702 In2iGui.Selection.Items.prototype = {
6703 	refresh : function() {
6704 		if (this.options.source) {
6705 			this.options.source.refresh();
6706 		}
6707 	},
6708 	objectsLoaded : function(objects) {
6709 		this.itemsLoaded(objects);
6710 	},
6711 	itemsLoaded : function(items) {
6712 		this.items = [];
6713 		this.element.update();
6714 		var self = this;
6715 		for (var i=0, len=items.length; i < len; ++i) {
6716 			var item = items[i];
6717 			var node = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_selection_item'});
6718 			var inner = new Element('span');
6719 			if (item.icon) {
6720 				inner.setStyle({'backgroundImage' : 'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(item.icon,1)+')'}).addClassName('in2igui_icon');
6721 			}
6722 			node.in2iGuiIndex = i;
6723 			node.insert(inner.insert(item.title));
6724 			this.element.insert(node);
6725 			node.observe('click',function() {
6726 				self.itemWasClicked(self.items[this.in2iGuiIndex].value);
6727 			});
6728 			node.ondblclick = function() {
6729 				self.itemWasDoubleClicked();
6730 				return false;
6731 			}
6732 			var info = {title:item.title,icon:item.icon,badge:item.badge,kind:item.kind,element:node,value:item.value};
6733 			node.dragDropInfo = info;
6734 			this.items.push(info);
6735 		};
6736 		this.updateUI();
6737 	},
6738 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
6739 		this.selection.changeValue(value);
6740 	},
6741 	itemWasDoubleClicked : function(node) {
6742 		this.selection.itemWasDoubleClicked();
6743 	},
6744 	getSelection : function() {
6745 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
6746 			if (this.items[i].value == this.selection.value) {
6747 				return this.items[i];
6748 			}
6749 		};
6750 		return null;
6751 	},
6752 	updateUI : function() {
6753 		var newValue = null;
6754 		this.items.each(function(item) {
6755 			if (item.value==this.selection.value) newValue=item.value;
6756 			item.element.setClassName('selected',(item.value==this.selection.value));
6757 		}.bind(this));
6758 		if (this.value!=newValue) {
6759 			this.value=newValue;
6760 			In2iGui.firePropertyChange(this,'value',this.value);
6761 		}
6762 	}
6763 }

6948 In2iGui.ImagePicker.prototype = {
6949 	addBehavior : function() {
6950 		var self = this;
6951 		this.element.onclick = function() {
6952 			self.showPicker();
6953 		}
6954 	},
6955 	setObject : function(obj) {
6956 		this.object = obj;
6957 		this.updateUI();
6958 	},
6959 	getObject : function() {
6960 		return this.object;
6961 	},
6962 	reset : function() {
6963 		this.object = null;
6964 		this.updateUI();
6965 	},
6966 	updateUI : function() {
6967 		if (this.object==null) {
6968 			this.element.style.backgroundImage='';
6969 		} else {
6970 			var url = In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'getImageUrl');
6971 			this.element.style.backgroundImage='url('+url+')';
6972 		}
6973 	},
6974 	showPicker : function() {
6975 		if (!this.picker) {
6976 			var self = this;
6977 			this.picker = In2iGui.BoundPanel.create();
6978 			this.content = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_imagepicker_thumbs'});
6979 			var buttons = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_imagepicker_buttons'});
6980 			var close = In2iGui.Button.create(null,{text:'Luk',highlighted:true});
6981 			close.addDelegate({
6982 				click:function() {self.hidePicker()}
6983 			});
6984 			var remove = In2iGui.Button.create(null,{text:'Fjern'});
6985 			remove.addDelegate({
6986 				click:function() {self.setObject(null);self.hidePicker()}
6987 			});
6988 			buttons.appendChild(close.getElement());
6989 			buttons.appendChild(remove.getElement());
6990 			this.picker.add(this.content);
6991 			this.picker.add(buttons);
6992 		}
6993 		this.picker.position(this.element);
6994 		this.picker.show();
6995 		if (!this.thumbnailsLoaded) {
6996 			this.updateImages();
6997 			this.thumbnailsLoaded = true;
6998 		}
6999 	},
7000 	hidePicker : function() {
7001 		this.picker.hide();
7002 	},
7003 	updateImages : function() {
7004 		var self = this;
7005 		var delegate = {
7006 			onSuccess:function(t) {
7007 				self.parse(t.responseXML);
7008 			}
7009 		};
7010 		new Ajax.Request(this.options.source,delegate);
7011 	},
7012 	parse : function(doc) {
7013 		this.content.update();
7014 		var images = doc.getElementsByTagName('image');
7015 		var self = this;
7016 		for (var i=0; i < images.length && i<50; i++) {
7017 			var id = images[i].getAttribute('id');
7018 			var url = '../../../util/images/?id='+id+'&maxwidth=48&maxheight=48&format=jpg';
7019 			var thumb = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_imagepicker_thumbnail'}).setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url('+url+')'});
7020 			thumb.in2iguiObject = {'id':id};
7021 			thumb.onclick = function() {
7022 				self.setObject(this.in2iguiObject);
7023 				self.hidePicker();
7024 			}
7025 			this.content.appendChild(thumb);
7026 		};
7027 	}
7028 }

7061 /********************************* Public methods ***********************************/
7062 
7063 In2iGui.BoundPanel.prototype = {
7064 	show : function() {
7065 		if (!this.visible) {
7066 			if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
7067 				n2i.setOpacity(this.element,0);
7068 			}
7069 			if (this.relativePosition=='left') {
7070 				this.element.style.marginLeft='30px';
7071 			} else {
7072 				this.element.style.marginLeft='-30px';
7073 			}
7074 			this.element.setStyle({
7075 				visibility : 'hidden', display : 'block'
7076 			})
7077 			var width = this.element.clientWidth;
7078 			this.element.setStyle({
7079 				width : width+'px' , visibility : 'visible'
7080 			});
7081 			this.element.style.marginTop='0px';
7082 			this.element.style.display='block';
7083 			if (!n2i.browser.msie) {
7084 				n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,400,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
7085 			}
7086 			n2i.ani(this.element,'margin-left','0px',800,{ease:n2i.ease.bounce});
7087 		}
7088 		this.element.style.zIndex = In2iGui.nextPanelIndex();
7089 		this.visible=true;
7090 	},
7091 	hide : function() {
7092 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {
7093 			this.element.style.display='none';
7094 		} else {
7095 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',0,300,{ease:n2i.ease.slowFast,hideOnComplete:true});
7096 		}
7097 		this.visible=false;
7098 	},
7099 	add : function(obj) {
7100 		if (obj.getElement) {
7101 			this.content.appendChild(obj.getElement());
7102 		} else {
7103 			this.content.appendChild(obj);
7104 		}
7105 	},
7106 	addSpace : function(height) {
7107 		this.add(new Element('div').setStyle({fontSize:'0px',height:height+'px'}));
7108 	},
7109 	getDimensions : function() {
7110 		if (this.element.style.display=='none') {
7111 			this.element.style.visibility='hidden';
7112 			this.element.style.display='block';
7113 			var width = this.element.getWidth();
7114 			var height = this.element.getHeight();
7115 			this.element.style.display='none';
7116 			this.element.style.visibility='';
7117 		} else {
7118 			var width = this.element.getWidth();
7119 			var height = this.element.getHeight();
7120 		}
7121 		return {width:width,height:height};
7122 	},
7123 	position : function(node) {
7124 		node = $(node);
7125 		var offset = node.cumulativeOffset();
7126 		var scrollOffset = node.cumulativeScrollOffset();
7127 		var dims = this.getDimensions();
7128 		var winWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth();
7129 		var nodeLeft = offset.left-scrollOffset.left+n2i.getScrollLeft();
7130 		var nodeWidth = node.getWidth();
7131 		var nodeHeight = node.getHeight();
7132 		var nodeTop = offset.top-scrollOffset.top+n2i.getScrollTop();
7133 		if ((nodeLeft+nodeWidth/2)/winWidth<.5) {
7134 			this.relativePosition='left';
7135 			var left = nodeLeft+nodeWidth+10;
7136 			this.arrow.className='arrow arrow_left';
7137 			var arrowLeft=-14;
7138 		} else {
7139 			this.relativePosition='right';
7140 			var left = nodeLeft-dims.width-10;
7141 			this.arrow.className='arrow arrow_right';
7142 			var arrowLeft=dims.width-4;
7143 		}
7144 		var top = Math.max(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2);
7145 		this.arrow.style.marginTop = (dims.height-32)/2+Math.min(0,nodeTop+(nodeHeight-dims.height)/2)+'px';
7146 		this.arrow.style.marginLeft = arrowLeft+'px';
7147 		if (this.visible) {
7148 			n2i.ani(this.element,'top',top+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
7149 			n2i.ani(this.element,'left',left+'px',500,{ease:n2i.ease.fastSlow});
7150 		} else {
7151 			this.element.style.top=top+'px';
7152 			this.element.style.left=left+'px';
7153 		}
7154 	}
7155 }

7213 In2iGui.RichText.prototype = {
7214 	isCompatible : function() {
7215 	    var agt=navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase();
7216 		return true;
7217 		return (agt.indexOf('msie 6')>-1 || agt.indexOf('msie 7')>-1 || (agt.indexOf('gecko')>-1 && agt.indexOf('safari')<0));
7218 	},
7219 	ignite : function() {
7220 		var self = this;
7221 		this.editor.observe("wysihat:loaded", function(event) {
7222 			this.editor.setStyle(this.options.style);
7223 			this.editor.setRawContent(this.value);
7224 			this.window = this.editor.getWindow();
7225 			this.document = this.editor.getDocument();
7226 			if (this.document.body) {
7227 				this.document.body.style.minHeight='100%';
7228 				this.document.body.style.margin='0';
7229 				this.document.documentElement.style.cursor='text';
7230 				this.document.documentElement.style.minHeight='100%';
7231 			}
7232 			Element.setStyle(this.document.body,this.options.style);
7233 			Event.observe(this.window,'focus',function() {self.documentFocused()});
7234 			Event.observe(this.window,'blur',function() {self.documentBlurred()});
7235 			this.ignited = true;
7236      	}.bind(this));
7237 		this.editor.observe("wysihat:change", function(event) {
7238         	this.documentChanged();
7239      	}.bind(this));
7240 	},
7241 	setHeight : function(height) {
7242 		this.editor.style.height=height+'px';
7243 	},
7244 	focus : function() {
7245 		try { // TODO : May only work in gecko
7246 			var r = this.document.createRange();
7247 			r.selectNodeContents(this.document.body);
7248 			this.window.getSelection().addRange(r);
7249 		} catch (ignore) {}
7250 		if (this.window)this.window.focus();
7251 	},
7252 	setValue : function(value) {
7253 		this.value = value;
7254 		this.editor.setRawContent(this.value);
7255 	},
7256 	getValue : function() {
7257 		return this.value;
7258 	},
7259 	deactivate : function() {
7260 		if (this.colorPicker) this.colorPicker.hide();
7261 		if (this.toolbar) this.toolbar.style.display='none';
7262 	},
7263 	
7264 	buildToolbar : function() {
7265 		this.toolbar.onmousedown = function() {this.toolbarMouseDown=true}.bind(this);
7266 		this.toolbar.onmouseup = function() {this.toolbarMouseDown=false}.bind(this);
7267 		var self = this;
7268 		var actions = In2iGui.RichText.actions;
7269 		for (var i=0; i < actions.length; i++) {
7270 			if (actions[i]==null) {
7271 				this.toolbarContent.insert(new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_richtext_divider'}));
7272 			} else {
7273 				var div = new Element('div').addClassName('action action_'+actions[i].key);
7274 				div.title=actions[i].key;
7275 				div.in2iguiRichTextAction = actions[i]
7276 				div.onclick = div.ondblclick = function(e) {return self.actionWasClicked(this.in2iguiRichTextAction,e);}
7277 				var img = new Element('img');
7278 				img.src=In2iGui.context+'/In2iGui/gfx/trans.png';
7279 				if (actions[i].icon) {
7280 					div.setStyle({'backgroundImage':'url('+In2iGui.getIconUrl(actions[i].icon,1)+')'});
7281 				}
7282 				div.insert(img);
7283 				this.toolbarContent.appendChild(div);
7284 				div.onmousedown = In2iGui.RichText.stopEvent;
7285 			}
7286 		};
7287 	},
7288 	documentFocused : function() {
7289 		if (n2i.browser.msie) {

7291 			return;
7292 		}
7293 		if (this.toolbar.style.display!='block') {
7294 			this.toolbar.style.marginTop='-40px';
7295 			n2i.setOpacity(this.toolbar,0);
7296 			this.toolbar.style.display='block';
7297 			n2i.ani(this.toolbar,'opacity',1,300);
7298 			n2i.ani(this.toolbar,'margin-top','-32px',300);
7299 		}
7300 	},
7301 	
7302 	documentBlurred : function() {
7303 		if (this.toolbarMouseDown) return;
7304 		if (this.options.autoHideToolbar) {
7305 			if (n2i.browser.msie) {
7306 				var self = this;
7307 				window.setTimeout(function() {
7308 					self.toolbar.style.display='none';
7309 				},100);
7310 				return;

7313 			n2i.ani(this.toolbar,'margin-top','-40px',300);
7314 		}

7317 	},

7323 		}
7324 	},

7327 		var evt = e ? e : window.event; 
7328 		if (evt.returnValue) {
7329 			evt.returnValue = false;
7330 		} else if (evt.preventDefault) {
7331 			evt.preventDefault( );
7332 		}
7333 		return false;
7334 	},

7338 			this.showColorPicker();
7339 		} else {

7342 		this.document.body.focus();
7343 		return false;
7344 	},

7346 		this.editor.execCommand(action.cmd,false,action.value);

7349 	showColorPicker : function() {

7353 			picker.addDelegate(this);
7354 			panel.add(picker);
7355 			panel.show();
7356 			this.colorPicker = panel;
7357 		}
7358 		this.colorPicker.show();
7359 	},
7360 	colorWasHovered : function(color) {
7361 		//this.document.execCommand('forecolor',false,color);
7362 	},
7363 	colorWasSelected : function(color) {
7364 		this.document.execCommand('forecolor',false,color);
7365 		this.documentChanged();

7398 	this.previousControl = this.element.select('.in2igui_imageviewer_previous')[0];
7399 	this.controller = this.element.select('.in2igui_imageviewer_controller')[0];
7400 	this.nextControl = this.element.select('.in2igui_imageviewer_next')[0];
7401 	this.playControl = this.element.select('.in2igui_imageviewer_play')[0];
7402 	this.text = this.element.select('.in2igui_imageviewer_text')[0];
7403 	this.dirty = false;
7404 	this.width = 600;
7405 	this.height = 460;
7406 	this.index = 0;
7407 	this.playing=false;
7408 	this.name = name;
7409 	this.images = [];
7410 	this.box.addDelegate(this);
7411 	this.addBehavior();
7412 	In2iGui.extend(this);
7413 }

7415 In2iGui.ImageViewer.create = function(name,options) {
7416 	options = options || {};
7417 	var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_imageviewer'});
7418 	element.update('<div class="in2igui_imageviewer_viewer"><div class="in2igui_imageviewer_inner_viewer"></div></div>'+

7423 	'<a class="in2igui_imageviewer_play"></a>'+
7424 	'<a class="in2igui_imageviewer_next"></a>'+
7425 	'</div>');
7426 	var box = In2iGui.Box.create(null,{absolute:true,modal:true});
7427 	box.add(element);

7433 In2iGui.ImageViewer.prototype = {
7434 	/** @private */
7435 	addBehavior : function() {
7436 		var self = this;
7437 		this.nextControl.onclick = function() {
7438 			self.next(true);
7439 		}
7440 		this.previousControl.onclick = function() {
7441 			self.previous(true);
7442 		}
7443 		this.playControl.onclick = function() {
7444 			self.playOrPause();
7445 		}
7446 		this.viewer.onclick = function() {
7447 			self.hide();
7448 		}
7449 		this.timer = function() {
7450 			self.next(false);
7451 		}
7452 		this.keyListener = function(e) {
7453 			if (n2i.isRightKey(e)) {
7454 				self.next(true);
7455 			} else if (n2i.isLeftKey(e)) {
7456 				self.previous(true);
7457 			} else if (n2i.isEscapeKey(e)) {
7458 				self.hide();
7459 			} else if (n2i.isReturnKey(e)) {
7460 				self.playOrPause();
7461 			}
7462 		}
7463 	},
7464 	/** @private */
7465 	getLargestSize : function(canvas,image) {
7466 		if (image.width<=canvas.width && image.height<=canvas.height) {
7467 			return {width:image.width,height:image.height};
7468 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height>image.width/image.height) {
7469 			return {width:canvas.height/image.height*image.width,height:canvas.height};
7470 		} else if (canvas.width/canvas.height<image.width/image.height) {
7471 			return {width:canvas.width,height:canvas.width/image.width*image.height};
7472 		} else {
7473 			return {width:canvas.width,height:canvas.height};
7474 		}
7475 	},
7476 	/** @private */
7477 	calculateSize : function() {
7478 		var snap = this.options.sizeSnap;
7479 		var newWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth()-this.options.perimeter;
7480 		newWidth = Math.floor(newWidth/snap)*snap;
7481 		newWidth = Math.min(newWidth,this.options.maxWidth);
7482 		var newHeight = n2i.getInnerHeight()-this.options.perimeter;
7483 		newHeight = Math.floor(newHeight/snap)*snap;
7484 		newHeight = Math.min(newHeight,this.options.maxHeight);
7485 		var maxWidth = 0;
7486 		var maxHeight = 0;
7487 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
7488 			var dims = this.getLargestSize({width:newWidth,height:newHeight},this.images[i]);
7489 			maxWidth = Math.max(maxWidth,dims.width);
7490 			maxHeight = Math.max(maxHeight,dims.height);
7491 		};
7492 		newHeight = Math.round(Math.min(newHeight,maxHeight));
7493 		newWidth = Math.round(Math.min(newWidth,maxWidth));
7494 		
7495 		if (newWidth!=this.width || newHeight!=this.height) {
7496 			this.width = newWidth;
7497 			this.height = newHeight;
7498 			this.dirty = true;
7499 		}
7500 	},
7501 	showById: function(id) {
7502 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
7503 			if (this.images[i].id==id) {
7504 				this.show(i);
7505 				break;
7506 			}
7507 		};
7508 	},
7509 	show: function(index) {
7510 		this.index = index || 0;
7511 		this.calculateSize();
7512 		this.updateUI();
7513 		var space = this.shouldShowController() ? 50 : 10;
7514 		this.element.setStyle({width:(this.width+10)+'px',height:(this.height+space)+'px'});
7515 		this.viewer.setStyle({width:(this.width+10)+'px',height:this.height+'px'});
7516 		this.innerViewer.setStyle({width:((this.width+10)*this.images.length)+'px',height:this.height+'px'});
7517 		this.controller.setStyle({paddingLeft:((this.width-115)/2+5)+'px'});
7518 		this.box.show();
7519 		this.goToImage(false,0,false);
7520 		Event.observe(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
7521 	},
7522 	hide: function(index) {
7523 		this.pause();
7524 		this.box.hide();
7525 		Event.stopObserving(document,'keydown',this.keyListener);
7526 	},
7527 	/** @private */
7528 	boxCurtainWasClicked : function() {
7529 		this.hide();
7530 	},
7531 	/** @private */
7532 	updateUI : function() {
7533 		if (this.dirty) {
7534 			this.innerViewer.innerHTML='';
7535 			for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
7536 				var url = this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[i]);
7537 				url = url.replace(/&/,'&');
7538 				var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_imageviewer_image'}).setStyle({'width':(this.width+10)+'px','height':this.height+'px'});
7539 				
7540 				var url = this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[i]);
7541 				url = url.replace(/&/g,'&');
7542 				this.innerViewer.appendChild(element);
7543 			};
7544 			if (this.shouldShowController()) {
7545 				this.controller.show();
7546 			} else {
7547 				this.controller.hide();
7548 			}
7549 			this.dirty = false;
7550 			this.preload();
7551 		}
7552 	},
7553 	/** @private */
7554 	shouldShowController : function() {
7555 		return this.images.length>1;
7556 	},
7557 	/** @private */
7558 	goToImage : function(animate,num,user) {	
7559 		if (animate) {
7560 			if (num>1) {
7561 				n2i.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+10),Math.min(num*this.options.transitionReturn,2000),{ease:this.options.easeReturn});				
7562 			} else {
7563 				var end = this.index==0 || this.index==this.images.length-1;
7564 				var ease = (end ? this.options.easeEnd : this.options.ease);
7565 				if (!user) ease = this.options.easeAuto;
7566 				n2i.ani(this.viewer,'scrollLeft',this.index*(this.width+10),(end ? this.options.transitionEnd : this.options.transition),{ease:ease});
7567 			}
7568 		} else {
7569 			this.viewer.scrollLeft=this.index*(this.width+10);
7570 		}
7571 		var text = this.images[this.index].text;
7572 		if (text) {
7573 			this.text.update(text).show();			
7574 		} else {
7575 			this.text.update().hide();
7576 		}
7577 	},
7578 	clearImages : function() {
7579 		this.images = [];
7580 		this.dirty = true;
7581 	},
7582 	addImages : function(images) {
7583 		for (var i=0; i < images.length; i++) {
7584 			this.addImage(images[i]);
7585 		};
7586 	},
7587 	addImage : function(img) {
7588 		this.images.push(img);
7589 		this.dirty = true;
7590 	},
7591 	/** @private */
7592 	resolveImageUrl : function(img) {
7593 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
7594 			if (this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl) {
7595 				return this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl(img,this.width,this.height);
7596 			}
7597 		};
7598 		return null;
7599 	},
7600 	play : function() {
7601 		if (!this.interval) {
7602 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
7603 		}
7604 		this.next(false);
7605 		this.playing=true;
7606 		this.playControl.className='in2igui_imageviewer_pause';
7607 	},
7608 	pause : function() {
7609 		window.clearInterval(this.interval);
7610 		this.interval = null;
7611 		this.playControl.className='in2igui_imageviewer_play';
7612 		this.playing = false;
7613 	},
7614 	playOrPause : function() {
7615 		if (this.playing) {
7616 			this.pause();
7617 		} else {
7618 			this.play();
7619 		}
7620 	},
7621 	resetPlay : function() {
7622 		if (this.playing) {
7623 			window.clearInterval(this.interval);
7624 			this.interval = window.setInterval(this.timer,6000);
7625 		}
7626 	},
7627 	previous : function(user) {
7628 		var num = 1;
7629 		this.index--;
7630 		if (this.index<0) {
7631 			this.index=this.images.length-1;
7632 			num = this.images.length-1;
7633 		}
7634 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
7635 		this.resetPlay();
7636 	},
7637 	next : function(user) {
7638 		var num = 1;
7639 		this.index++;
7640 		if (this.index==this.images.length) {
7641 			this.index=0;
7642 			num = this.images.length-1;
7643 		}
7644 		this.goToImage(true,num,user);
7645 		this.resetPlay();
7646 	},
7647 	/** @private */
7648 	preload : function() {
7649 		var guiLoader = new n2i.Preloader();
7650 		guiLoader.addImages(In2iGui.context+'In2iGui/gfx/imageviewer_controls.png');
7651 		var self = this;
7652 		guiLoader.setDelegate({allImagesDidLoad:function() {self.preloadImages()}});
7653 		guiLoader.load();
7654 	},
7655 	/** @private */
7656 	preloadImages : function() {
7657 		this.loader = new n2i.Preloader();
7658 		this.loader.setDelegate(this);
7659 		for (var i=0; i < this.images.length; i++) {
7660 			this.loader.addImages(this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[i]));
7661 		};
7662 		this.status.innerHTML = '0%';
7663 		this.status.style.display='';
7664 		this.loader.load();
7665 	},
7666 	/** @private */
7667 	allImagesDidLoad : function() {
7668 		this.status.style.display='none';
7669 	},
7670 	/** @private */
7671 	imageDidLoad : function(loaded,total,index) {
7672 		this.status.innerHTML = Math.round(loaded/total*100)+'%';
7673 		var url = this.resolveImageUrl(this.images[index]);
7674 		url = url.replace(/&/g,'&');
7675 		this.innerViewer.childNodes[index].style.backgroundImage="url('"+url+"')";
7676 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_abort',false);
7677 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_error',false);
7678 	},
7679 	/** @private */
7680 	imageDidGiveError : function(loaded,total,index) {
7681 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_error',true);
7682 	},
7683 	/** @private */
7684 	imageDidAbort : function(loaded,total,index) {
7685 		Element.setClassName(this.innerViewer.childNodes[index],'in2igui_imageviewer_image_abort',true);
7686 	}
7687 }

7721 In2iGui.Picker.prototype = {
7722 	addBehavior : function() {
7723 		var self = this;
7724 		this.content.observe('mousedown',function(e) {
7725 			self.startDrag(e);
7726 			return false;
7727 		});
7728 	},
7729 	setObjects : function(objects) {
7730 		this.selected = null;
7731 		this.objects = objects || [];
7732 		this.updateUI();
7733 	},
7734 	setValue : function(value) {
7735 		this.value = value;
7736 		this.updateSelection();
7737 	},
7738 	reset : function() {
7739 		this.value = null;
7740 		this.updateSelection();
7741 	},
7742 	updateUI : function() {
7743 		var self = this;
7744 		this.content.update();
7745 		this.container.scrollLeft=0;
7746 		this.container.setStyle({width:this.options.itemsVisible*(this.options.itemWidth+14)+'px'});
7747 		this.container.style.height=(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px';
7748 		this.content.style.width=(this.objects.length*(this.options.itemWidth+14))+'px';
7749 		this.content.style.height=(this.options.itemHeight+10)+'px';
7750 		this.objects.each(function(object,i) {
7751 			var item = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_picker_item',title:object.title});
7752 			if (self.value!=null && object[self.options.valueProperty]==self.value) item.addClassName('in2igui_picker_item_selected');
7753 			item.update(
7754 				'<div class="in2igui_picker_item_middle"><div class="in2igui_picker_item_middle">'+
7755 				'<div style="width:'+self.options.itemWidth+'px;height:'+self.options.itemHeight+'px;background-image:url(\''+object.image+'\')"></div>'+
7756 				'</div></div>'+
7757 				'<div class="in2igui_picker_item_bottom"><div><div></div></div></div>'
7758 			);
7759 			item.observe('mouseup',function() {self.selectionChanged(object[self.options.valueProperty])});
7760 			self.content.insert(item);			
7761 		});
7762 	},
7763 	updateSelection : function() {
7764 		var children = this.content.childNodes;
7765 		for (var i=0; i < children.length; i++) {
7766 			Element.setClassName(children[i],'in2igui_picker_item_selected',this.value!=null && this.objects[i][this.options.valueProperty]==this.value);
7767 		};
7768 	},
7769 	selectionChanged : function(value) {
7770 		if (this.dragging) return;
7771 		if (this.value==value) return;
7772 		this.value = value;
7773 		this.updateSelection();
7774 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'selectionChanged',value);
7775 	},
7776 	
7777 	// Dragging
7778 	startDrag : function(e) {
7779 		e.stop();
7780 		var self = this;
7781 		this.dragX = Event.pointerX(e);
7782 		this.dragScroll = this.container.scrollLeft;
7783 		In2iGui.Picker.mousemove = function(e) {self.drag(e);return false;}
7784 		In2iGui.Picker.mouseup = In2iGui.Picker.mousedown = function(e) {self.endDrag(e);return false;}
7785 		window.document.observe('mousemove',In2iGui.Picker.mousemove);
7786 		window.document.observe('mouseup',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
7787 		window.document.observe('mousedown',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
7788 	},
7789 	drag : function(e) {
7790 		this.dragging = true;
7791 		Event.stop(e);
7792 		this.container.scrollLeft=this.dragX-e.pointerX()+this.dragScroll;
7793 	},
7794 	endDrag : function(e) {
7795 		this.dragging = false;
7796 		Event.stop(e);
7797 		window.document.stopObserving('mousemove',In2iGui.Picker.mousemove);
7798 		window.document.stopObserving('mouseup',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
7799 		window.document.stopObserving('mousedown',In2iGui.Picker.mouseup);
7800 		var size = (this.options.itemWidth+14);
7801 		n2i.ani(this.container,'scrollLeft',Math.round(this.container.scrollLeft/size)*size,500,{ease:n2i.ease.bounceOut});
7802 	}
7803 }

7824 In2iGui.Editor.prototype = {
7825 	ignite : function() {
7826 		this.reload();
7827 	},
7828 	addPartController : function(key,title,controller) {
7829 		this.partControllers.push({key:key,'title':title,'controller':controller});
7830 	},
7831 	getPartController : function(key) {
7832 		var ctrl = null;
7833 		this.partControllers.each(function(item) {
7834 			if (item.key==key) ctrl=item;
7835 		});
7836 		return ctrl;
7837 	},
7838 	reload : function() {
7839 		if (this.partControls) {
7840 			this.partControls.hide();
7841 		}
7842 		var self = this;
7843 		this.parts = [];
7844 		var rows = $$('.row');
7845 		rows.each(function(row,i) {
7846 			var columns = row.select('.column');
7847 			self.reloadColumns(columns,i);
7848 			columns.each(function(column,j) {
7849 				var parts = column.select('.part');
7850 				self.reloadParts(parts,i,j);
7851 			});
7852 		});
7853 		var parts = $$('.part');
7854 		
7855 		this.parts.each(function(part) {
7856 			var i = parts.indexOf(part.element);
7857 			if (i!=-1) delete(parts[i]);
7858 		});
7859 		this.reloadParts(parts,-1,-1);
7860 	},
7861 	partExists : function(element) {
7862 		
7863 	},
7864 	reloadColumns : function(columns,rowIndex) {
7865 		var self = this;
7866 		columns.each(function(column,columnIndex) {
7867 			column.observe('mouseover',function() {
7868 				self.hoverColumn(column);
7869 			});
7870 			column.observe('mouseout',function() {
7871 				self.blurColumn();
7872 			});
7873 			column.observe('contextmenu',function(e) {
7874 				self.contextColumn(column,rowIndex,columnIndex,e);
7875 			});
7876 		});
7877 	},
7878 	reloadParts : function(parts,row,column) {
7879 		var self = this;
7880 		parts.each(function(element,partIndex) {
7881 			if (!element) return;
7882 			var match = element.className.match(/part_([\w]+)/i);
7883 			if (match && match[1]) {
7884 				var handler = self.getPartController(match[1]);
7885 				if (handler) {
7886 					var part = new handler.controller(element,row,column,partIndex);
7887 					part.type=match[1];
7888 					element.observe('click',function() {
7889 						self.editPart(part);
7890 					});
7891 					element.observe('mouseover',function(e) {
7892 						self.hoverPart(part);
7893 					});
7894 					element.observe('mouseout',function(e) {
7895 						self.blurPart(e);
7896 					});
7897 					element.observe('mousedown',function(e) {
7898 						self.startPartDrag(e);
7899 					});
7900 					self.parts.push(part);
7901 				}
7902 			}
7903 		});
7904 	},
7905 	activate : function() {
7906 		this.active = true;
7907 	},
7908 	deactivate : function() {
7909 		this.active = false;
7910 		if (this.activePart) {
7911 			this.activePart.deactivate();
7912 		}
7913 		if (this.partControls) this.partControls.hide();
7914 	},
7915 	
7916 	
7917 	///////////////////////// Columns ////////////////////////
7918 	
7919 	hoverColumn : function(column) {
7920 		this.hoveredColumn = column;

7939 				menu.addItem({title:item.title,value:item.key});
7940 			});

7949 		if (value=='removeColumn') {
7950 			this.fire('removeColumn',{'row':this.hoveredRow,'column':this.hoveredColumnIndex});
7951 		} else if (value=='editColumn') {
7952 			this.editColumn(this.hoveredRow,this.hoveredColumnIndex);
7953 		} else if (value=='addColumn') {
7954 			this.fire('addColumn',{'row':this.hoveredRow,'position':this.hoveredColumnIndex+1});
7955 		} else {

7957 		}

8213 In2iGui.Editor.startDrag = function(e,element) {
8214 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement = element;
8215 	Element.observe(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.Editor.dragListener);
8216 	Element.observe(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener);
8217 	In2iGui.Editor.startDragPos = {top:e.pointerY(),left:e.pointerX()};
8218 	e.stop();
8219 	return false;
8220 }
8221 
8222 In2iGui.Editor.dragListener = function(e) {
8223 	var element = In2iGui.Editor.dragElement;
8224 	element.style.left = e.pointerX()+'px';
8225 	element.style.top = e.pointerY()+'px';
8226 	element.style.display='block';
8227 	return false;
8228 }
8229 
8230 In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener = function(event) {
8231 	Event.stopObserving(document.body,'mousemove',In2iGui.Editor.dragListener);
8232 	Event.stopObserving(document.body,'mouseup',In2iGui.Editor.dragEndListener);
8233 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement.style.display='none';
8234 	In2iGui.Editor.dragElement=null;
8235 }
8236 
8237 In2iGui.Editor.getPartId = function(element) {
8238 	var m = element.id.match(/part\-([\d]+)/i);
8239 	if (m && m.length>0) return m[1];
8240 }

8244 In2iGui.Editor.Header = function(element,row,column,position) {
8245 	this.element = $(element);
8246 	this.row = row;
8247 	this.column = column;
8248 	this.position = position;
8249 	this.id = In2iGui.Editor.getPartId(this.element);
8250 	this.header = this.element.firstDescendant();
8251 	this.field = null;
8252 }
8253 
8254 In2iGui.Editor.Header.prototype = {
8255 	activate : function() {
8256 		this.value = this.header.innerHTML;
8257 		this.field = new Element('textarea').addClassName('in2igui_editor_header');
8258 		this.field.value = this.value;
8259 		this.header.style.visibility='hidden';
8260 		this.updateFieldStyle();
8261 		this.element.insertBefore(this.field,this.header);
8262 		this.field.focus();
8263 		this.field.select();
8264 		this.field.observe('keydown',function(e) {
8265 			if (e.keyCode==Event.KEY_RETURN) {
8266 				this.save();
8267 			}
8268 		}.bind(this));
8269 	},
8270 	save : function() {
8271 		var value = this.field.value;
8272 		this.header.innerHTML = value;
8273 		this.deactivate();
8274 		if (value!=this.value) {
8275 			this.value = value;
8276 			In2iGui.Editor.get().partChanged(this);
8277 		}
8278 	},
8279 	cancel : function() {
8280 		this.deactivate();
8281 	},
8282 	deactivate : function() {
8283 		this.header.style.visibility='';
8284 		this.element.removeChild(this.field);
8285 		In2iGui.Editor.get().partDidDeacivate(this);
8286 	},
8287 	updateFieldStyle : function() {
8288 		this.field.setStyle({width:this.header.getWidth()+'px',height:this.header.getHeight()+'px'});
8289 		n2i.copyStyle(this.header,this.field,['fontSize','marginTop','fontWeight','fontFamily','textAlign','color','fontStyle']);
8290 	},
8291 	getValue : function() {
8292 		return this.value;
8293 	}
8294 }

8307 In2iGui.Editor.Html.prototype = {
8308 	activate : function() {
8309 		this.value = this.element.innerHTML;
8310 		//if (Prototype.Browser.IE) return;
8311 		var height = this.element.getHeight();
8312 		this.element.update('');
8313 		var style = this.buildStyle();
8314 		this.editor = In2iGui.RichText.create(null,{autoHideToolbar:false,style:style});
8315 		this.editor.setHeight(height);
8316 		this.element.appendChild(this.editor.getElement());
8317 		this.editor.addDelegate(this);
8318 		this.editor.ignite();
8319 		this.editor.setValue(this.value);
8320 		this.editor.focus();
8321 	},
8322 	buildStyle : function() {
8323 		return {
8324 			'textAlign':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'text-align')
8325 			,'fontFamily':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-family')
8326 			,'fontSize':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-size')
8327 			,'fontWeight':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'font-weight')
8328 			,'color':n2i.getStyle(this.element,'color')
8329 		}
8330 	},
8331 	cancel : function() {
8332 		this.deactivate();
8333 		this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
8334 	},
8335 	save : function() {
8336 		this.deactivate();
8337 		var value = this.editor.value;
8338 		if (value!=this.value) {
8339 			this.value = value;
8340 			In2iGui.Editor.get().partChanged(this);
8341 		}
8342 		this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
8343 	},
8344 	deactivate : function() {
8345 		if (this.editor) {
8346 			this.editor.deactivate();
8347 			this.element.innerHTML = this.value;
8348 		}
8349 		In2iGui.Editor.get().partDidDeacivate(this);
8350 	},
8351 	richTextDidChange : function() {
8352 		//this.deactivate();
8353 	},

8356 	}

8360 In2iGui.Menu = function(element,name,options) {
8361 	this.options = n2i.override({autoHide:false,parentElement:null},options);
8362 	this.element = $(element);
8363 	this.name = name;
8364 	this.value = null;
8365 	this.subMenus = [];
8366 	this.visible = false;
8367 	In2iGui.extend(this);
8368 	this.addBehavior();
8369 }
8370 
8371 In2iGui.Menu.create = function(name,options) {
8372 	options = options || {};
8373 	var element = new Element('div').addClassName('in2igui_menu');
8374 	var obj = new In2iGui.Menu(element,name,options);
8375 	document.body.appendChild(element);
8376 	return obj;
8377 }
8378 
8379 In2iGui.Menu.prototype = {
8380 	addBehavior : function() {
8381 		var self = this;
8382 		this.hider = function() {
8383 			self.hide();
8384 		}
8385 		if (this.options.autoHide) {
8386 			var x = function(e) {
8387 				if (!In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.element) && (!self.options.parentElement || !In2iGui.isWithin(e,self.options.parentElement))) {
8388 					if (!self.isSubMenuVisible()) {
8389 						self.hide();
8390 					}
8391 				}
8392 			};
8393 			this.element.observe('mouseout',x);
8394 			if (this.options.parentElement) {
8395 				this.options.parentElement.observe('mouseout',x);
8396 			}
8397 		}
8398 	},
8399 	addDivider : function() {
8400 		this.element.insert(new Element('div').addClassName('in2igui_menu_divider'));
8401 	},
8402 	addItem : function(item) {
8403 		var self = this;
8404 		var element = new Element('div').addClassName('in2igui_menu_item').update(item.title);
8405 		element.observe('click',function(e) {
8406 			self.itemWasClicked(item.value);
8407 			Event.stop(e);
8408 		});
8409 		if (item.children) {
8410 			var sub = In2iGui.Menu.create(null,{autoHide:true,parentElement:element});
8411 			sub.addItems(item.children);
8412 			element.observe('mouseover',function(e) {
8413 				sub.showAtElement(element,e,'horizontal');
8414 			});
8415 			//sub.addDelegate({itemWasClicked:function(value) {self.itemWasClicked(value)}});
8416 			self.subMenus.push(sub);
8417 			element.addClassName('in2igui_menu_item_children');
8418 		}
8419 		this.element.insert(element);
8420 	},
8421 	addItems : function(items) {
8422 		for (var i=0; i < items.length; i++) {
8423 			if (items[i]==null) {
8424 				this.addDivider();
8425 			} else {
8426 				this.addItem(items[i]);
8427 			}
8428 		};
8429 	},
8430 	getValue : function() {
8431 		return this.value;
8432 	},
8433 	itemWasClicked : function(value) {
8434 		this.value = value;
8435 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'itemWasClicked',value);
8436 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'select',value);
8437 		this.hide();
8438 	},
8439 	showAtPointer : function(event) {
8440 		if (event) {
8441 			Event.stop(event);
8442 			//if (event.type!='click') this.ignoreNextClick=true;
8443 		}
8444 		this.showAtPoint({'top':event.pointerY(),'left':event.pointerX()});
8445 	},
8446 	showAtElement : function(element,event,position) {
8447 		if (event) {
8448 			Event.stop(event);
8449 		}
8450 		var point = element.cumulativeOffset();
8451 		if (position=='horizontal') {
8452 			point.left += element.getWidth();
8453 		} else if (position=='vertical') {
8454 			point.top += element.getHeight();
8455 		}
8456 		this.showAtPoint(point);
8457 	},
8458 	showAtPoint : function(pos) {
8459 		var innerWidth = n2i.getInnerWidth();
8460 		var innerHeight = n2i.getInnerHeight();
8461 		var scrollTop = n2i.getScrollTop();
8462 		var scrollLeft = n2i.getScrollLeft();
8463 		if (!this.visible) {
8464 			this.element.setStyle({'display':'block','visibility':'hidden',opacity:0});
8465 		}
8466 		var width = this.element.getWidth();
8467 		var height = this.element.getHeight();
8468 		this.element.setStyle({'top':Math.min(pos.top,innerHeight-height-20+scrollTop)+'px','left':Math.min(pos.left,innerWidth-width-20+scrollLeft)+'px','visibility':'visible',zIndex:In2iGui.nextTopIndex()});
8469 		if (!this.visible) {
8470 			n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',1,200);
8471 			this.addHider();
8472 			this.visible = true;
8473 		}
8474 	},
8475 	hide : function() {
8476 		if (!this.visible) return;
8477 		var self = this;
8478 		n2i.ani(this.element,'opacity',0,200,{onComplete:function() {
8479 			self.element.setStyle({'display':'none'});
8480 		}})
8481 		this.removeHider();
8482 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
8483 			this.subMenus[i].hide();
8484 		};
8485 		this.visible = false;
8486 	},
8487 	isSubMenuVisible : function() {
8488 		for (var i=0; i < this.subMenus.length; i++) {
8489 			if (this.subMenus[i].visible) return true;
8490 		};
8491 		return false;
8492 	},
8493 	addHider : function() {
8494 		Element.observe(document.body,'click',this.hider);
8495 	},
8496 	removeHider : function() {
8497 		Event.stopObserving(document.body,'click',this.hider);
8498 	}
8499 }

8526 				// TODO: should be unreg'ed but it fails

8531 			}
8532 		}
8533 		this.element.observe('mouseout',this.hider);
8534 	},

8569 		this.visible = true;

8572 			element.observe('mouseout',this.hider);
8573 			element.addClassName('in2igui_overlay_bound');
8574 		}

8619 In2iGui.Upload.prototype = {
8620 	addBehavior : function() {
8621 		var self = this;
8622 		if (!this.flashMode) {
8623 			this.createIframeVersion();
8624 			return;
8625 		}
8626 		if (In2iGui.get().domLoaded) {
8627 			this.createFlashVersion();			
8628 		} else {
8629 			In2iGui.onDomReady(function() {self.createFlashVersion()});
8630 		}
8631 	},

8633 	/////////////////////////// Iframe //////////////////////////
8634 	
8635 	createIframeVersion : function() {
8636 		var container = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_upload'});
8637 		var form = new Element('form',{'action':this.options.url || '', 'method':'post', 'enctype':'multipart/form-data','encoding':'multipart/form-data','target':'upload'});
8638 		if (this.options.parameters) {
8639 			$H(this.options.parameters).each(function(pair) {
8640 				var hidden = new Element('input',{'type':'hidden','name':pair.key});
8641 				hidden.setValue(pair.value);
8642 				form.insert(hidden);
8643 			});
8644 		}
8645 		var file = new Element('input',{'type':'file','class':'file','name':this.options.name});
8646 		var self = this;
8647 		file.onchange = function() {self.iframeSubmit()}
8648 		form.insert(file);
8649 		container.insert(form);
8650 		var iframe = new Element('iframe',{name:'upload',id:'upload'}).setStyle({display:'none'});
8651 		iframe.observe('load',function() {self.iframeUploadComplete()});
8652 		container.insert(iframe);
8653 		this.progressBar = In2iGui.ProgressBar.create();
8654 		this.progressBar.hide();
8655 		container.insert(this.progressBar.getElement());
8656 		this.form = form;
8657 		this.element.insert(container);
8658 	},
8659 	iframeUploadComplete : function() {
8660 		if (!this.uploading) return;
8661 		this.uploading = false;
8662 		this.form.reset();
8663 		this.fire('uploadDidCompleteQueue');
8664 	},
8665 	iframeSubmit : function() {
8666 		this.uploading = true;
8667 		// IE: set value of parms again since they disappear
8668 		var p = this.options.parameters;
8669 		for (var i=0; i < p.length; i++) {
8670 			this.form[p[i].name].value=p[i].value;
8671 		};
8672 		this.form.submit();
8673 		this.fire('uploadDidSubmit');
8674 	},
8675 	startProgress : function() {
8676 		this.form.style.display='none';
8677 		this.progressBar.show();
8678 	},
8679 	setProgress : function(value) {
8680 		this.progressBar.setValue(value);
8681 	},
8682 	endProgress : function() {
8683 		this.form.style.display='block';
8684 		this.form.reset();
8685 		this.progressBar.reset();
8686 		this.progressBar.hide();
8687 	},
8688 	
8689 	parentShown : function() {
8690 		this.updateButtonPosition();
8691 	},
8692 	clear : function() {
8693 		for (var i=0; i < this.items.length; i++) {
8694 			if (this.items[i]) {
8695 				this.items[i].destroy();
8696 			}
8697 		};
8698 		this.items = [];
8699 		this.itemContainer.hide();
8700 		this.status.update();
8701 	},

8703 	/////////////////////////// Flash //////////////////////////
8704 	
8705 	createFlashVersion : function() {
8706 		var loc = new String(document.location);
8707 		var url = loc.slice(0,loc.lastIndexOf('/')+1);
8708 		url += this.options.url;
8709 		var session = n2i.cookie.get('JSESSIONID');
8710 		if (session) {
8711 			url+=';jsessionid='+session;

8714 		var size = {width:108,height:28};
8715 		var self = this;
8716 		this.loader = new SWFUpload({
8717 			upload_url : url,
8718 			flash_url : In2iGui.context+"/In2iGui/lib/swfupload/swfupload.swf",
8719 			file_size_limit : "20480",
8720 			file_upload_limit : 100,
8721 			debug : true,
8722 			post_params : this.options.parameters,
8723 			button_placeholder_id : 'x',
8724 			button_placeholder : this.element.select('.in2igui_upload_placeholder')[0],
8725 			button_width : size.width,
8726 			button_height : size.height,
8727 
8728 			swfupload_loaded_handler : function() {self.flashLoaded()},
8729 			file_queued_handler : self.fileQueued.bind(self),
8730 			file_queue_error_handler : function(file, error, message) {self.fileQueueError(file, error, message)},
8731 			file_dialog_complete_handler : function() {self.fileDialogComplete()},
8732 			upload_start_handler : function() {self.uploadStart()},
8733 			upload_progress_handler : function(file,complete,total) {self.uploadProgress(file,complete,total)},
8734 			upload_error_handler : function(file, error, message) {self.uploadError(file, error, message)},
8735 			upload_success_handler : function(file,data) {self.uploadSuccess(file,data)},
8736 			upload_complete_handler : function(file) {self.uploadComplete(file)},
8737 		
8738 			// SWFObject settings
8739 			swfupload_pre_load_handler : function() {alert('swfupload_pre_load_handler!')},
8740 			swfupload_load_failed_handler : function() {alert('swfupload_load_failed_handler!')}
8741 		});
8742 		if (this.options.button) {
8743 			this.setButton(In2iGui.get(this.options.button));
8744 		}
8745 	},
8746 	setButton : function(widget) {
8747 		this.button = widget;
8748 		if (this.button && this.flashMode) {
8749 			var m = this.element.select('object')[0].remove();
8750 			m.setStyle({width:'108px','marginLeft':'-108px',position:'absolute'});
8751 			widget.getElement().insert(m);
8752 			return;
8753 		}
8754 	},
8755 	updateButtonPosition : function() {
8756 		if (this.button) {
8757 			var f = this.button.element.select('object')[0];
8758 			if (f) {
8759 				var w = this.button.element.getWidth();
8760 				f.setStyle({width:w+'px','marginLeft':'-'+w+'px',position:'absolute'})
8761 			}
8762 		}
8763 	},
8764 	startNextUpload : function() {
8765 		this.loader.startUpload();
8766 	},
8767 	addError : function(error,file) {
8768 		var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_upload_item_error'});
8769 		element.insert(new Element('a',{'class':'in2igui_link'}).update('<span>Fjern</span>').observe('click',function() {this.parentNode.remove(); return false;}));
8770 		element.insert('<strong>'+In2iGui.Upload.errors[error]+'</strong><br/><em>'+file.name+'</em>');
8771 		this.itemContainer.insert(element);
8772 	},

8774 	//////////////////// Events //////////////
8775 	
8776 	flashLoaded : function() {
8777 		this.loaded = true;
8778 	},
8779 	fileQueued : function(file) {
8780 		var item = new In2iGui.Upload.Item(file);
8781 		this.items[file.index] = item;
8782 		this.itemContainer.insert(item.element);
8783 		this.itemContainer.setStyle({display:'block'});
8784 	},
8785 	fileQueueError : function(file, error, message) {
8786 		this.addError(error,file);
8787 	},
8788 	fileDialogComplete : function() {
8789 		this.startNextUpload();
8790 	},
8791 	uploadStart : function() {
8792 		if (!this.busy) {
8793 			this.fire('uploadDidStartQueue');
8794 		}
8795 		this.busy = true;
8796 	},
8797 	uploadProgress : function(file,complete,total) {
8798 		this.updateStatus();
8799 		this.items[file.index].updateProgress(complete,total);
8800 	},
8801 	uploadError : function(file, error, message) {
8802 		if (file) {
8803 			this.items[file.index].update(file);
8804 		}
8805 	},
8806 	uploadSuccess : function(file,data) {
8807 		this.items[file.index].updateProgress(file.size,file.size);
8808 	},
8809 	uploadComplete : function(file) {
8810 		this.items[file.index].update(file);
8811 		this.startNextUpload();
8812 		var self = this;
8813 		this.fire('uploadDidComplete',file);
8814 		if (this.loader.getStats().files_queued==0) {
8815 			this.fire('uploadDidCompleteQueue');
8816 		}
8817 		this.updateStatus();
8818 		this.busy = false;
8819 	},
8820 	
8821 	/// Status ///
8822 	updateStatus : function() {
8823 		var s = this.loader.getStats();
8824 		this.status.update('Status: '+Math.round(s.successful_uploads/this.items.length*100)+'%');
8825 		n2i.log(s);
8826 	}
8827 }

8893 /* EOF *//** A progress bar is a widget that shows progress from 0% to 100%
8894 	@constructor
8895 */
8896 In2iGui.ProgressBar = function(o) {
8897 	this.element = $(o.element);
8898 	this.name = o.name;
8899 	/** @private */
8900 	this.WAITING = 'in2igui_progressbar_small_waiting';
8901 	/** @private */
8902 	this.COMPLETE = 'in2igui_progressbar_small_complete';
8903 	/** @private */
8904 	this.options = o || {};
8905 	/** @private */
8906 	this.indicator = this.element.firstDescendant();
8907 	In2iGui.extend(this);
8908 }
8909 
8910 /** Creates a new progress bar:
8911 	@param o {Object} Options : {small:false}
8912 */
8913 In2iGui.ProgressBar.create = function(o) {
8914 	o = o || {};
8915 	var e = o.element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_progressbar'}).insert(new Element('div'));
8916 	if (o.small) e.addClassName('in2igui_progressbar_small');
8917 	return new In2iGui.ProgressBar(o);
8918 }
8919 	
8920 In2iGui.ProgressBar.prototype = {
8921 	/** Set the progress value
8922 	@param value {Number} A number between 0 and 1
8923 	*/
8924 	setValue : function(value) {
8925 		var el = this.element;
8926 		if (this.waiting) el.removeClassName(this.WAITING);
8927 		el.setClassName(this.COMPLETE,value==1);
8928 		n2i.ani(this.indicator,'width',(value*100)+'%',200);
8929 	},
8930 	/** Mark progress as waiting */
8931 	setWaiting : function() {
8932 		this.waiting = true;
8933 		this.indicator.setStyle({width:0});
8934 		this.element.addClassName(this.WAITING);
8935 	},
8936 	/** Reset the progress bar */
8937 	reset : function() {
8938 		var el = this.element;
8939 		if (this.waiting) el.removeClassName(this.WAITING);
8940 		el.removeClassName(this.COMPLETE);
8941 		this.indicator.style.width='0%';
8942 	},
8943 	/** Hide the progress bar */
8944 	hide : function() {
8945 		this.element.style.display = 'none';
8946 	},
8947 	/** Show the progress bar */
8948 	show : function() {
8949 		this.element.style.display = 'block';
8950 	}

8953 /* EOF */In2iGui.Gallery = function(id,name,options) {
8954 	this.id = id;
8955 	this.name = name;
8956 	this.options = options || {};
8957 	this.element = $(id);
8958 	this.objects = [];
8959 	this.nodes = [];
8960 	this.selected = new Hash();
8961 	this.width = 100;
8962 	this.height = 100;
8963 	In2iGui.extend(this);

8965 
8966 In2iGui.Gallery.prototype = {
8967 	setObjects : function(objects) {
8968 		this.objects = objects;
8969 		this.render();
8970 	},
8971 	getObjects : function() {
8972 		return this.objects;
8973 	},
8974 	render : function() {
8975 		this.nodes = [];
8976 		this.element.update();
8977 		var self = this;
8978 		this.objects.each(function(object,i) {
8979 			var url = self.resolveImageUrl(object);
8980 			url = url.replace(/&/,'&');
8981 			if (object.height<object.width) {
8982 				var top = (self.height-(self.height*object.height/object.width))/2;
8983 			} else {
8984 				var top = 0;
8985 			}
8986 			var img = new Element('img',{src:url}).setStyle({margin:top+'px auto 0px'});
8987 			var item = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_gallery_item'}).setStyle({'width':self.width+'px','height':self.height+'px'}).insert(img);
8988 			item.observe('click',function() {
8989 				self.itemClicked(i);
8990 			});
8991 			item.observe('dblclick',function() {
8992 				self.itemDoubleClicked(i);
8993 			});
8994 			self.element.insert(item);
8995 			self.nodes.push(item);
8996 		});
8997 	},
8998 	updateUI : function() {
8999 		var self = this;
9000 		this.objects.each(function(object,i) {
9001 			if (self.selected.get(i)) {
9002 				self.nodes[i].addClassName('in2igui_gallery_item_selected');
9003 			} else {
9004 				self.nodes[i].removeClassName('in2igui_gallery_item_selected');
9005 			}
9006 		});
9007 	},
9008 	resolveImageUrl : function(img) {
9009 		for (var i=0; i < this.delegates.length; i++) {
9010 			if (this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl) {
9011 				return this.delegates[i].resolveImageUrl(img,this.width,this.height);
9012 			}
9013 		};
9014 		return '';
9015 	},
9016 	itemClicked : function(index) {
9017 		this.selected = new Hash();
9018 		this.selected.set(index,true);
9019 		this.updateUI();
9020 	},
9021 	itemDoubleClicked : function(index) {

9023 	}

9039 In2iGui.Calendar.prototype = {
9040 	getFirstDay : function() {
9041 		var date = new Date(this.date.getTime());
9042 		date.setDate(date.getDate()-date.getDay()+1);
9043 		date.setHours(0);
9044 		date.setMinutes(0);
9045 		date.setSeconds(0);
9046 		return date;
9047 	},
9048 	getLastDay : function() {
9049 		var date = new Date(this.date.getTime());
9050 		date.setDate(date.getDate()-date.getDay()+7);
9051 		date.setHours(23);
9052 		date.setMinutes(59);
9053 		date.setSeconds(59);
9054 		return date;
9055 	},
9056 	clearEvents : function() {
9057 		this.events = [];
9058 		var nodes = this.element.select('.in2igui_calendar_event');
9059 		nodes.each(function(node) {
9060 			node.remove();
9061 		});
9062 		this.hideEventViewer();
9063 	},
9064 	setEvents : function(events) {
9065 		this.setBusy(false);
9066 		this.clearEvents();
9067 		this.events = events;
9068 		var self = this;
9069 		var pixels = (this.options.endHour-this.options.startHour)*40;
9070 		this.events.each(function(event) {
9071 			var day = self.body.select('.day')[event.startTime.getDay()-1];
9072 			var node = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event'});
9073 			var top = ((event.startTime.getHours()*60+event.startTime.getMinutes())/60-self.options.startHour)*40-1;
9074 			var height = (event.endTime.getTime()-event.startTime.getTime())/1000/60/60*40+1;
9075 			var height = Math.min(pixels-top,height);
9076 			node.setStyle({'marginTop':top+'px','height':height+'px'});
9077 			var content = new Element('div');
9078 			content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_time'}).update(event.startTime.dateFormat('H:i')));
9079 			content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_text'}).update(event.text));
9080 			if (event.location) {
9081 				content.insert(new Element('p',{'class':'in2igui_calendar_event_location'}).update(event.location));
9082 			}
9083 			day.insert(node.insert(content));
9084 			node.observe('click',function() {
9085 				self.eventWasClicked(event,this);
9086 			});
9087 		});
9088 	},

9095 		} else {
9096 			this.element.removeClassName('in2igui_calendar_busy');
9097 		}
9098 	},

9103 		
9104 		var days = this.head.select('.day');
9105 		for (var i=0; i < days.length; i++) {
9106 			var date = new Date(first.getTime());
9107 			date.setDate(date.getDate()+i);
9108 			days[i].update(date.dateFormat('l \\d. d M'))
9109 		};
9110 	},
9111 	buildUI : function() {
9112 		var bar = this.element.select('.in2igui_calendar_bar')[0];
9113 		this.toolbar = In2iGui.Toolbar.create(null,{labels:false});
9114 		bar.insert(this.toolbar.getElement());

9119 		today.addDelegate(this);
9120 		this.toolbar.add(today);
9121 		var next = In2iGui.Button.create('in2iguiCalendarNext',{text:'',icon:'monochrome/next'});

9130 			var node = new Element('div').update('<span><em>'+i+':00</em></span>');

9133 			}
9134 			if (i==this.options.endHour) {

9138 		};
9139 	},

9229 In2iGui.DatePicker = function(id,name,options) {
9230 	this.name = name;
9231 	this.element = $(id);
9232 	this.options = {};
9233 	n2i.override(this.options,options);
9234 	this.cells = [];
9235 	this.title = this.element.select('strong')[0];
9236 	this.today = new Date();
9237 	this.value = this.options.value ? new Date(this.options.value.getTime()) : new Date();
9238 	this.viewDate = new Date(this.value.getTime());

9245 In2iGui.DatePicker.create = function(name,options) {
9246 	var element = new Element('div',{'class':'in2igui_datepicker'});
9247 	element.insert('<div class="in2igui_datepicker_header"><a class="in2igui_datepicker_next"></a><a class="in2igui_datepicker_previous"></a><strong></strong></div>');
9248 	var table = new Element('table');
9249 	var head = new Element('tr');
9250 	table.insert(new Element('thead').insert(head));
9251 	for (var i=0;i<7;i++) {
9252 		head.insert(new Element('th').update(Date.dayNames[i].substring(0,3)));
9253 	}
9254 	var body = new Element('tbody');
9255 	table.insert(body);
9256 	for (var i=0;i<6;i++) {
9257 		var row = new Element('tr');
9258 		for (var j=0;j<7;j++) {
9259 			var cell = new Element('td');
9260 			row.insert(cell);
9261 		}
9262 		body.insert(row);
9263 	}
9264 	element.insert(table);
9265 	return new In2iGui.DatePicker(element,name,options);
9266 }

9268 In2iGui.DatePicker.prototype = {
9269 	addBehavior : function() {
9270 		var self = this;
9271 		this.cells = this.element.select('td');
9272 		this.cells.each(function(cell,index) {
9273 			cell.observe('mousedown',function() {self.selectCell(index)});
9274 		})
9275 		this.element.select('.in2igui_datepicker_next')[0].observe('mousedown',function() {self.next()});
9276 		this.element.select('.in2igui_datepicker_previous')[0].observe('mousedown',function() {self.previous()});
9277 	},
9278 	setValue : function(date) {
9279 		this.value = new Date(date.getTime());
9280 		this.viewDate = new Date(date.getTime());
9281 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
9282 		this.updateUI();
9283 	},
9284 	updateUI : function() {
9285 		this.title.update(this.viewDate.dateFormat('F Y'));
9286 		var isSelectedYear =  this.value.getFullYear()==this.viewDate.getFullYear();
9287 		var month = this.viewDate.getMonth();
9288 		for (var i=0; i < this.cells.length; i++) {
9289 			var date = this.indexToDate(i);
9290 			var cell = this.cells[i];
9291 			if (date.getMonth()<month) {
9292 				cell.className = 'in2igui_datepicker_dimmed';
9293 			} else if (date.getMonth()>month) {
9294 				cell.className = 'in2igui_datepicker_dimmed';
9295 			} else {
9296 				cell.className = '';
9297 			}
9298 			if (date.getDate()==this.value.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.value.getMonth() && isSelectedYear) {
9299 				cell.addClassName('in2igui_datepicker_selected');
9300 			}
9301 			if (date.getDate()==this.today.getDate() && date.getMonth()==this.today.getMonth() && date.getFullYear()==this.today.getFullYear()) {
9302 				cell.addClassName('in2igui_datepicker_today');
9303 			}
9304 			cell.update(date.getDate());
9305 		};
9306 	},
9307 	getPreviousMonth : function() {
9308 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
9309 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()-1);
9310 		return previous;
9311 	},
9312 	getNextMonth : function() {
9313 		var previous = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
9314 		previous.setMonth(previous.getMonth()+1);
9315 		return previous;
9316 	},
9317 	////////////////// Events ///////////////
9318 	previous : function() {
9319 		this.viewDate = this.getPreviousMonth();
9320 		this.updateUI();
9321 	},
9322 	next : function() {
9323 		this.viewDate = this.getNextMonth();
9324 		this.updateUI();
9325 	},
9326 	selectCell : function(index) {
9327 		this.value = this.indexToDate(index);
9328 		this.viewDate = new Date(this.value.getTime());
9329 		this.viewDate.setDate(1);
9330 		this.updateUI();
9331 		In2iGui.callDelegates(this,'dateChanged',this.value);
9332 	},
9333 	indexToDate : function(index) {
9334 		var first = this.viewDate.getDay();
9335 		var days = this.viewDate.getDaysInMonth();
9336 		var previousDays = this.getPreviousMonth().getDaysInMonth();
9337 		if (index<first) {
9338 			var date = this.getPreviousMonth();
9339 			date.setDate(previousDays-first+index+1);
9340 			return date;
9341 		} else if (index>first+days-1) {
9342 			var date = this.getPreviousMonth();
9343 			date.setDate(index-first-days+1);
9344 			return date;
9345 			cell.update(i-first-days+1);
9346 		} else {
9347 			var date = new Date(this.viewDate.getTime());
9348 			date.setDate(index+1-first);
9349 			return date;
9350 		}
9351 	}
9352 }

9471 		var w = e.getWidth();
9472 		var top = (n2i.getInnerHeight()-e.getHeight())/2+n2i.getScrollTop();
9473 		e.setStyle({'marginLeft':(w/-2)+'px',top:top+'px'});
9474 		e.setStyle({display:'block',visibility:'visible'});
9475 	},
